val result = f_fact.
  join(dim_location, $"f_fact.location_id" === $"dim_location.location_id").
  join(dim_time, $"f_fact.dt" === $"dim_time.dt").
  join(dim_price, $"f_fact.price_id" === $"dim_price.price_id").
//   where($"year" === 2019).
  groupBy($"dim_time.month", $"dim_location.country", $"price_range").
  agg(sum($"available_count").as("available_sum"), sum($"not_available_count").as("not_available_sum")).
  select($"dim_time.month", $"dim_location.country", ($"not_available_sum" / ($"available_sum" + $"not_available_sum")).as("percent"), $"price_range").
//   groupBy($"month", $"country").
//   agg($"available_sum", $"not_available_sum", $"percent").
  orderBy($"month", $"percent".desc)
  
result.createOrReplaceTempView("resultTable")

%md
Zależność między ceną a liczbą pokoi i łazienek po kraju i roku 
cena(miara), liczba pokoi(wymiar), kraj(seria - wymiar), rok (selekcja)

val result3 = f_fact.
  join(dim_location, $"f_fact.location_id" === $"dim_location.location_id").
  join(dim_time, $"f_fact.dt" === $"dim_time.dt").
//   join(dim_price, $"f_fact.price_id" === $"dim_price.price_id").
  groupBy($"dim_time.year", $"dim_location.country", $"bathrooms").
  agg(sum($"sum_price").as("sum_price"), sum($"available_count").as("available_sum"), sum($"not_available_count").as("not_available_sum")).
  select($"dim_time.year", $"dim_location.country", $"bathrooms", ($"sum_price" / ($"available_sum" + $"not_available_sum")).as("avg_price")).
  orderBy($"year")
  
result3.createOrReplaceTempView("resultTable3")
